<br>
Before focus items casters had their preferance of gear.  Some liked Int, saves, stamina, others likes AC, mana and HPS, or any combonation of the six, or more.  Now add to that some focus effects put on pretty crappy caster items and you'll get even more variety.<br>
<br>
Those that know what they want will excell, those that don't and are frantic to get it all will have all the charm of a barnyard chicken.<br>
<br>
 <p>Antra Immortalis <BR> Member of the Phoenix Crusaders <BR> Arch Mage of Mithaniel Marr <BR> E. Marr Server<BR>Magelo: <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=142225">Antra</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uguildon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Guildon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 194<br> <font color=#E9D756>(6/10/02 7:24:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3394.topic&index=43>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: !</span><hr size=1> A lot of people griping here and it's all seemingly for naught. Why in the world is everyone complaing about these focus items? Do you feel that you are underpowered compared to melee classes? I mean come on. Wizards do obscene damage, clerics can cheal like nobody's business. Mages and necros are broken. Shamans are ridiculously stong. Druids are a bit lacking. Enchanters are valuable no matter what. Just think of these specialities as equipment upgrades. <br>
<br>
I'm failing to understand the gripes of casting classes as being underpowered or unbalanced. Like I said mages and necros are broken. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uantradawnryder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Antra Dawnryder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 90<br> <font color=#E9D756>(6/10/02 11:52:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3394.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: !</span><hr size=1> I&quot;M BROKEN!<br>
<br>
